00:25:49,381 --> 00:25:52,217
<i>We can still ruin Kyle</i>
<i>even if you say nothing.</i>

470
00:25:55,262 --> 00:25:56,805
<i>Did you think you got me already?</i>

471
00:25:56,888 --> 00:25:58,807
<i>Watch out and I'll get my revenge.</i>

472
00:25:58,890 --> 00:26:01,810
<i>What if he acted on</i>
<i>his threats towards Louisa?</i>
